## Three.js starter npm

A basic three.js project with ES6 support.

- npm for dependencies
- mocha for testing
- babel/webpack for compiling, building and packing
- eslint airbnb base configuration

First, install npm dependencies
```

npm install
```

Run the tests
```

npm run test
```

Watch the tests
```

npm run test:watch
```

Build the app
```

npm run build
```

Watch for changes on source and build
```

npm run build:watch
```


